    en.lproj/Localizable.strings. Android resource names = the iOS key with
    '.' replaced by '_'. Format specifiers: iOS %@ -> Android %1$s, %d kept.
    Apostrophes are escaped (\') as required by Android string resources.
    The two record.save.* strings are Android-adapted (Files app path wording
    replaced with the on-device app storage equivalent) while keeping meaning
    and the %1$s file-name argument.
-->
